desc: Wildthings Natural Bugspray - Fiercely effective against mosquitoes, ticks, flies, ants and more. Wildthings natural insect repellent is 100% natural and non-toxic, contains no synthetic chemicals, additives, or preservatives. DEET-free and Cruelty-free. Wildthings' ingredients are skin-nourishing and smell wonderful!
